items.title: Blackstone said to emerge as lead bidder for Haldiram stake
items.description: Talks are advanced and the parties are looking to reach an agreement as soon as the coming weeks, the people said, adding that other bidders remain interested in potentially buying a stake.

items.title: Serum Institute of India to make mpox vaccine for Denmark's Bavarian Nordic
items.description: Bavarian will transfer the technology to Serum Institute to supply the shots for Indian market. Serum Institute will also carry out contract manufacturing on profit-sharing model for Bavarian Nordic to help expand global capacity.

items.title: Vedanta approves fourth interim dividend of Rs 8.5 per share amounting to Rs 3,324 crore
items.description: Vedanta approves fourth interim dividend of Rs 8.5 per share amounting to Rs 3,324 crore

items.title: HDFC Bank gets administrative warning from Sebi over delayed disclosure of mortgage head's resignation in March
items.description: Sebi also said that the lender further violated regulations by failing to explain the reason for the delay in filing the disclosure in this regard.

items.title: Qatar agrees to supply LNG to Gail India in five-year deal
items.description: Gail India will receive one LNG shipment a month from April 2025 until March 2030, people familiar with the development told Bloomberg News. The deal was concluded as part of a tender that closed earlier this month.

items.title: HPCL lines up Rs 4,679 crore modernization at Mumbai refinery, lasting four years, to ramp up lube production
items.description: HPCL’s lubricants also cater to emerging transport solutions such BS-VI, CNG and electric vehicles (EVs) and is also exported globally to over 30 countries including USA.
